## Phase 6: Security & Compliance (Hardening)
- **KeyVault**: Centralized secret management for Gemini, Mistral, and Kaggle.
- **Audit Logging**: Every API interaction is recorded to `audit_logs.jsonl` with latency and status.
- **Rate Limiting**: [JudgeGuard](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/scripts/judge_guard.py#82-465) now enforces daily budgets to prevent cost overruns and API suspensions.
- **Client Refactoring**: [GeminiClient](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/src/antigravity_core/gemini_client.py#9-140) and [MistralClient](file:///home/kizabgd/Desktop/Istrazivanje/src/antigravity_core/mistral_client.py#17-149) fully integrated with the security layer.
